::DevilDuer/FZ/Zardus::

DevilDuer slammed into a wall as a panel detatched itself from the cealing 
and hit him. He jumps up and runs after Serpentor, rubbing his head.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zardus stops near the exit. He looks at FZ. "Has he been here?"

FZ shakes his head.

"Go find him. I'll guard the exit." Zardus says and pushes a button on the 
controlls. The doors shut.

FZ runs off down a hallway, homing in on Serpentor's signiture.
